					function IconStream(width, height, stream) {
						this.width = width;
						this.height = height;
						var count = 0;

						function get(bytes) {
							return (count &gt; stream.length) ? "" : stream.slice(count, count += bytes);
						};
						this.read = function (bytes) {
							return get(bytes);
						};
					}

This allows the form to concatenate them into the narrative in a grammatically correct way.\n\n- Be sure to read through generated portions of the narrative carefully. The form cannot account for all possible scenarios and will require user input in areas.\n\n- If you \"Recreate\" the narrative after pushing the button once, it will erase any user input and cannot be undone.\n\n***It is ALWAYS recommended to use a completely blank form for each report. 	function iText(num) {
		var arr = ["Test"];
		for (var i = 0; i &lt; parseInt(num); i++) {
			arr.push("This is a test narrative");
		}
		return  arr.join(". ").toString() + ".";
	};

               <script contentType="application/x-javascript">function cFields(vis) {
	var iFields = [
		"FTN_Sway_",
		"FTN_Pad_",
		"FTN_Searched_",
		"FTN_Eyes_",
		"FTN_Wrong_",
		"FTN_Down_",
	];
	var oFields = [];
	for (var i = 0; i &lt; iFields.length; i++) {
		for (var o = 1; o &lt; 7; o++) {
			oFields.push(iFields[i]+o);
		};
	};
	for (var x = 0; x &lt; oFields.length; x++) {
		xfa.resolveNode(oFields[x]).presence = vis;
	};
	FTN_Not_Given.presence = vis;
	FTN_Line.presence = vis == "hidden" ? "visible" : "hidden";
};

if ($.rawValue == "1") {
	cFields("hidden");
} else {
	cFields("visible");
};
</script>

               <script contentType="application/x-javascript">var iArray = [
	"CNS_Depressant",
	"CNS_Stimulant",
	"Hallucinogen",
	"Dissociative_Anesthetic",
	"Narcotic_Analgesic",
	"Inhalant",
	"Cannabis",
];

function checkImpairment() {
	for (var i = 0; i &lt; iArray.length; i++) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode(iArray[i]).rawValue == 1) {
			return true;
			break;
		} else {
			continue;
		};
	};
};

if (checkImpairment() == true) {
	Medical.presence = "hidden";
	Not_Impaired.presence = "hidden";
} else {
	Medical.presence = "visible";
	Not_Impaired.presence = "visible";
};
</script>

										},

											width: 5,
											type: "radio",
											item_id: "rad6",
											name: "N/A",
											group_id: "grp1",
										},
									]
								},
								{
									type: "view",
									item_id: "vie6",
									elements: [{
										type: "static_text",
										item_id: "sta7",
										name: "What did the subject's eyes do?",
									}]
								},
								{
									type: "view",
									item_id: "vie7",
									align_children: "align_row",
									elements: [{
											type: "static_text",

										},

							width: 110,
							type: "gap",

							type: "ok_cancel",
							ok_name: "Create Narrative",
						},
						{
							width: 10,
							height: 1,
							type: "edit_text",
							item_id: "edi4",
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		initialize: function (dialog) {
			dialog.load({
				"pop1": dialogObject.pop1,
				"edi3": dialogObject.edi3,
				"edi1": dialogObject.edi1,
				"ed10": dialogObject.ed10,
				"ed11": dialogObject.ed11,
				"edi2": dialogObject.edi2,
				"edi5": dialogObject.edi5,
				"edi6": dialogObject.edi6,
				"rad1": dialogObject.rad1,
				"rad2": dialogObject.rad2,
				"sta8": "Left Eye:",
				"edi7": dialogObject.edi7,
				"edi8": dialogObject.edi8,
				"rad3": dialogObject.rad3,
				"rad4": dialogObject.rad4,
				"edi4": dialogObject.edi4,
				"rad5": dialogObject.rad5,
				"rad6": dialogObject.rad6,
			});
			dialog.enable({
				"edi5": false,
			});
			dialog.visible({
				"sta7": false,
				"sta8": false,
				"edi7": false,
				"sta9": false,
				"edi8": false,
				"edi4": false
			});
			if (popInInst == "PBT") {
				dialog.enable({
					"edi6": false
				});
			};
		},
		validate: function (dialog) {
			//add validate code here
			return true;
		},
		commit: function (dialog) {
			var elements = dialog.store();
			dialogObject.pop1 = elements["pop1"];
			dialogObject.edi3 = elements["edi3"];
			dialogObject.edi1 = elements["edi1"];
			dialogObject.ed10 = elements["ed10"];
			dialogObject.ed11 = elements["ed11"];
			dialogObject.edi2 = elements["edi2"];
			dialogObject.edi5 = elements["edi5"];
			dialogObject.edi6 = elements["edi6"];
			dialogObject.rad1 = elements["rad1"];
			dialogObject.rad2 = elements["rad2"];
			dialogObject.edi7 = elements["edi7"];
			dialogObject.edi8 = elements["edi8"];
			dialogObject.rad3 = elements["rad3"];
			dialogObject.rad4 = elements["rad4"];
			dialogObject.edi4 = elements["edi4"];
			dialogObject.rad5 = elements["rad5"];
			dialogObject.rad6 = elements["rad6"];
		},
		cancel: function (dialog) {
			dialog.end("cancel")
		},
		"clu1": function (dialog) {},
		"vie1": function (dialog) {},
		"pop1": function (dialog) {
			var lst1 = dialog.store()["pop1"];
			for (var item in lst1) {
				if (lst1[item] &gt; 0) {
					var selectedValue = item;
					break;
				}
			}
			dialog.load({
				"edi4": selectedValue
			});
		},
		"edi3": function (dialog) {},
		"vie2": function (dialog) {},
		"edi1": function (dialog) {},
		"ed10": function (dialog) {},
		"ed11": function (dialog) {},
		"clu2": function (dialog) {},
		"edi2": function (dialog) {},
		"clu3": function (dialog) {},
		"vie3": function (dialog) {},
		"edi5": function (dialog) {},
		"vie4": function (dialog) {},
		"edi6": function (dialog) {},
		"clu4": function (dialog) {},
		"vie5": function (dialog) {},
		"rad1": function (dialog) {
			dialog.visible({
				sta7: true,
				sta8: true,
				sta9: true,
				edi7: true,
				edi8: true
			});
		},
		"rad2": function (dialog) {
			dialog.visible({
				sta7: false,
				sta8: false,
				sta9: false,
				edi7: false,
				edi8: false
			});
		},
		"rad3": function (dialog) {
			dialog.visible({
				sta7: false,
				sta8: false,
				sta9: false,
				edi7: false,
				edi8: false
			});
		},
		"vie6": function (dialog) {},
		"vie7": function (dialog) {},
		"edi7": function (dialog) {},
		"vie8": function (dialog) {},
		"edi8": function (dialog) {},
		"rad3": function (dialog) {},
		"rad4": function (dialog) {},
		"edi4": function (dialog) {},
		"rad5": function (dialog) {},
		"rad6": function (dialog) {},
	};
	var dialogObject = {
		pop1: stateOut,
		edi3: popInCounty,
		edi1: popInPlace,
		ed10: "",
		ed11: "",
		edi2: "SUBJECT",
		edi5: serialMod,
		edi6: instMod,
		rad1: false,
		rad2: false,
		edi7: "",
		edi8: "",
		rad3: false,
		rad4: false,
		edi4: stateMod,
		rad5: false,
		rad6: false,
		execDialog: function () {
			return app.execDialog(dialogDescriptor);
		},
		selectedItem: function (control) {
			if (typeof (control) === "string") {
				control = this[control];
			}
			for (var item in control) {
				if (typeof (control[item]) === "object") {
					var r = this.selectedItem(control[item]);
					if (r !== undefined) {
						return r;
					}
				} else {
					if (control[item] &gt; 0) {
						return control[item];
					}
				}
			}
		}
	};
	return dialogObject;
};
var d = dialog()

/*==========================================================================================
 POST-COMMIT ACTIONS
 ==========================================================================================*/

if (d.execDialog() !== "cancel") {

	var oConvergenceRight = d.edi8.toLowerCase();

	} else {

	}

	} else {
		var skipConj = false;
	};

	} else {
		var oAverageVsExpected = "average";
	}

	var his_her = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Subject_Gender").rawValue == null ? '!GENDER MISSING!' : (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Subject_Gender").rawValue == "M" ? 'his' : 'her');
	var oNameS = oName.toLowerCase().endsWith("s") ? oName + '\'' : oName + '\'s';

	} else {

	}

	} else {

" + "The psychophysical tests were conducted " + oPhysical + ". The darkroom examination was conducted " + oDark + ". This evaluation started on " + _startDate_ + " at " + _startTime_ + " and was completed on [DATE] at " + _endTime_ + ".");

	if ((results_ == "????") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Breath_Instrument").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Breath_Refused").rawValue !== 1)) {

	/*==========================================================================================

	var myArrayObs = [];

	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Attitude").rawValue !== null) {
		var attitude = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Attitude").rawValue.toLowerCase().split(',').map(function (reduce) {
			return reduce.trim();
		});
		if (attitude.length == 2) {
			var attitude = attitude.join(' and ').toString();
		} else if (attitude.length &gt;= 3) {
			var attitude = attitude.join(', ').replace(/, ([^,]*)$/, ', and $1').toString();
		}
		myArrayObs.push(oNameS + " attitude was " + attitude);
	}

	// Cooperation

	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Coordination").rawValue !== null) {

			return reduce.trim();

		}
		myArrayMed.push(oName + " told me " + he_she + " is not taking any medications and/or drugs, but stated the following: [" + drugs + "].");
	} else if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Meds_Drugs").rawValue == 2) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Meds_Drugs_Notes").rawValue == null)) {
		myArrayMed.push(oName + " told me " + he_she + " is not taking any medications and/or drugs.");
	}

			7. PSYCHOPHYSICAL INDICATORS OF IMAPIRMENT

Prior to attempting each test, " + oName + " advised " + he_she + " understood the instructions. Unless otherwise noted, the following tests were administered to " + oName + ":");

	//
	//------Modified Romberg Balance-------------//
	//

	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.MRB_Refused").rawValue == 1) {
		var MRB_Text = (oName + " refused to perform this test");
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_2.TextField10").rawValue = MRB_Text;
	} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.MRB_NotGiven").rawValue == 1) {
		var MRB_Text = ("This test was not administered to " + oName + " because [EXPLAIN]");
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_2.TextField10").rawValue = MRB_Text;
	} else {
		var MRB_Est = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.MRB_Time").rawValue;
		if (MRB_Est !== null) {
			if (MRB_Est &lt;= 24) {
				var pace = "slow";
			} else if (MRB_Est &gt;= 36) {
				var pace = "fast";
			} else {
				var pace = "approximate"
			}
			var MRB_Text = (oNameS + " internal time estimation was " + pace + ", estimating "  + MRB_Est + " seconds in 30 seconds.");
			xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_2.TextField10").rawValue = MRB_Text;
		}
	}

	//
	//------Walk and Turn-------------//
	//

	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Refused").rawValue !== 1) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_NotGiven").rawValue !== 1)) { // === If WAT Refused and WAT Not given are not checked
		//
		var myArrayWAT = [];
		var myArrayTotalWAT = [];

		//-------Instruction

		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Balance").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Too_Soon").rawValue !== null)) { // IF EITHER INSTRUCTION STAGE CLUE BOXES ARE CHECKED
			if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Balance").rawValue !== null) {
				myArrayWAT.push("could not keep balance during instructions");
			}
			if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Too_Soon").rawValue !== null) {
				myArrayWAT.push("started walking too soon");
			}
			var arrRes = myArrayWAT.join(' and ') + ".";
			if (myArrayWAT !== "") {
				myArrayTotalWAT.push(oName + " " + arrRes);
			}
		}

		//
		//------- First Set of Steps
		//

		var myArrayWAT = [];
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_1").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " stopped while walking after steps [STEPS]");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_1").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " missed heel-to-toe between steps [STEPS]");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_1").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " stepped off line on steps [STEPS]");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_1").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " raised " + his_her + " arms for balance");
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== null)) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " took the wrong number of steps");
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== null)) {
			var myArrayWAT = [myArrayWAT.join('. ').toString() + ('.')];
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== null) {
			var firstNumSteps = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue;
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " took a total of " + firstNumSteps + " steps.");
			var myArrayWAT = [myArrayWAT.join(" ").toString()];
		} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue == null) {
			var firstNumSteps = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue;
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " took a total of ???? steps.");
			var myArrayWAT = [myArrayWAT.join(" ").toString()];
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_1").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_1").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_1").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_1").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue == 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== null)) {
			myArrayTotalWAT.push("On the first set of steps, " + myArrayWAT);
		} else if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_1").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_1").rawValue !== null)) {
			myArrayTotalWAT.push("On the first set of steps, " + myArrayWAT);
		}

		//	
		//-------TURN
		//

		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Turn").rawValue !== null) {
			var turnDesc = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Turn").rawValue.toLowerCase();
			myArrayTotalWAT.push(oName + " performed the turn [" + turnDesc + "].");
		}

		//
		//------- Second Set of Steps
		//

		var myArrayWAT = [];
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_2").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " stopped while walking after steps [STEPS]");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_2").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " missed heel-to-toe between steps [STEPS]");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_2").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " stepped off line on steps [STEPS]");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_2").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " raised " + his_her + " arms for balance");
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== null)) {
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " took the wrong number of steps");
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== null)) {
			var myArrayWAT = [myArrayWAT.join('. ').toString() + ('.')];
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== null) {
			var secondNumSteps = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue;
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " took a total of " + secondNumSteps + " steps.");
			var myArrayWAT = [myArrayWAT.join(" ").toString()];
		} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue == null) {
			var secondNumSteps = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue;
			myArrayWAT.push(oName + " took a total of ???? steps.");
			var myArrayWAT = [myArrayWAT.join(" ").toString()];
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_2").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_2").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_2").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_2").rawValue == null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue == 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== null)) {
			myArrayTotalWAT.push("On the second set of steps, " + myArrayWAT);
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Stops_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Miss_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Off_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Arms_2").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== 9) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Steps_2").rawValue !== null)) {
			myArrayTotalWAT.push("On the second set of steps, " + myArrayWAT);
		}
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_4.TextField11").rawValue = myArrayTotalWAT.join('\n\n').toString();
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_Refused").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_4.TextField11").rawValue = (oName + " refused to perform this test.");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.WAT_NotGiven").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_4.TextField11").rawValue = ("This test was not administered to " +
			oName + " because [explain].");
	}

	//
	//---------------------------One Leg Stand Left -------------------------//
	//

	var myArrayOLSL = [];
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Sway").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Arms").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Hop").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Down").rawValue !== null)) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Sway").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSL.push("swayed while balancing");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Arms").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSL.push("used " + his_her + " arms for balance");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Hop").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSL.push("hopped");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Down").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSL.push("put " + his_her + " foot down at [COUNT]");
		}
		var myArrayOLSL = ["While performing this test, " + oName + " " + myArrayOLSL.join(', ').replace(/, ([^,]*)$/, ', and $1').toString() + (".")];
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Count").rawValue !== null) {
		myArrayOLSL.push(oNameS + " ending count was [" + xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Count").rawValue + "].");
	}
	xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_6.TextField12").rawValue = myArrayOLSL.join(' ').toString();

	//
	//---------------------------One Leg Stand Right-------------------------//
	//

	var myArrayOLSR = [];
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Sway").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Arms").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Hop").rawValue !== null) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Down").rawValue !== null)) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Sway").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSR.push("swayed while balancing");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Arms").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSR.push("used " + his_her + " arms for balance");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Hop").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSR.push("hopped");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Down").rawValue !== null) {
			myArrayOLSR.push("put " + his_her + " foot down at [COUNT]");
		}
		var myArrayOLSR = ["While performing this test, " + oName + " " + myArrayOLSR.join(', ').replace(/, ([^,]*)$/, ', and $1').toString() + (".")];
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Count").rawValue !== null) {
		myArrayOLSR.push(oNameS + " ending count was [" + xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Count").rawValue + "].");
	}
	xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_8.TextField13").rawValue = myArrayOLSR.join(' ').toString();

	///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Refused").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_6.TextField12").rawValue = (oName + " refused to perform this test.");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Refused").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_8.TextField13").rawValue = (oName + " refused to perform this test.");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_L_Not_Given").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_6.TextField12").rawValue = ("This test was not administered to " + oName + " because [EXPLAIN].");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.OLS_R_Not_Given").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.N_7_8.TextField13").rawValue = ("This test was not administered to " + oName + " because [EXPLAIN].");
	}

	//
	//---------------------------Finger to nose-------------------------------------------------------
	//

	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Refused").rawValue !== 1) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Not_Given").rawValue !== 1)) {
		var tp1 = (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Pad_1").rawValue == 1) ? "pad" : "tip";
		var tp2 = (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Pad_2").rawValue == 1) ? "pad" : "tip";
		var tp3 = (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Pad_3").rawValue == 1) ? "pad" : "tip";
		var tp4 = (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Pad_4").rawValue == 1) ? "pad" : "tip";
		var tp5 = (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Pad_5").rawValue == 1) ? "pad" : "tip";
		var tp6 = (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Pad_6").rawValue == 1) ? "pad" : "tip";

		function iFTN(num) {
			var sway = "topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Sway_".concat(num);
			var searched = "topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Searched_".concat(num);
			var eyes = "topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Eyes_".concat(num);
			var wrong = "topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Wrong_".concat(num);
			var down = "topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Down_".concat(num);
			if ((xfa.resolveNode(sway).rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode(searched).rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode(eyes).rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode(wrong).rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode(down).rawValue == 1)) {
				var FTN_Arr = [];
				if (xfa.resolveNode(sway).rawValue == 1) {
					FTN_Arr.push("swayed");
				}
				if (xfa.resolveNode(searched).rawValue == 1) {
					FTN_Arr.push("searched for " + his_her + " nose");
				}
				if (xfa.resolveNode(eyes).rawValue == 1) {
					FTN_Arr.push("closed " + his_her + " eyes");
				}
				if (xfa.resolveNode(wrong).rawValue == 1) {
					FTN_Arr.push("started with the wrong hand");
				}
				if (xfa.resolveNode(down).rawValue == 1) {
					FTN_Arr.push("had to be told to put " + his_her + " hand down");
				}
				if (FTN_Arr.length == 2) {
					var join = FTN_Arr.join(' and ').toString() + ".";
				} else if (FTN_Arr.length &gt;= 3) {
					var join = FTN_Arr.join(', ').replace(/, ([^,]*)$/, ', and $1').toString() + ".";
				} else {
					var join = FTN_Arr + ".";
				}
				return ("During this test " + oName + " " + join)
			} else {
				return "";
			}
		}

		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.F4.TextField5").rawValue = (
			"#1 - " + oName + " touched the " + tp1 + " of " + his_her + " left finger to [DESCRIBE]. " + iFTN("1") + "\n\n" +
			"#2 - " + oName + " touched the " + tp2 + " of " + his_her + " right finger to [DESCRIBE]. " + iFTN("2") + "\n\n" +
			"#3 - " + oName + " touched the " + tp3 + " of " + his_her + " left finger to [DESCRIBE]. " + iFTN("3") + "\n\n" +
			"#4 - " + oName + " touched the " + tp4 + " of " + his_her + " right finger to [DESCRIBE]. " + iFTN("4") + "\n\n" +
			"#5 - " + oName + " touched the " + tp5 + " of " + his_her + " right finger to [DESCRIBE]. " + iFTN("5") + "\n\n" +
			"#6 - " + oName + " touched the " + tp6 + " of " + his_her + " left finger to [DESCRIBE]. " + iFTN("6"));
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Refused").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.F4.TextField5").rawValue = (oName + " refused to perform this test.");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.FTN_Not_Given").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_7.F4.TextField5").rawValue = ("This test was not administered to" + oName + " because [EXPLAIN].");
	}

	/*==========================================================================================
		8. CLINICAL INDICATORS							
	=========================================================================================*/
	//

	//-------------------------------- HGN ---------------------------------------//

	var myArrHGN = [];
	var arrRes = "";
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Pupil_Size").rawValue !== null) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Pupil_Size").rawValue == 1 ? myArrHGN.push(oName + " had equal pupil sizes") : myArrHGN.push(oName + " had unequal pupil sizes");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Tracking").rawValue !== null) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Tracking").rawValue == 1 ? myArrHGN.push(oName + " had equal tracking") : myArrHGN.push(oName + " had unequal tracking");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Able_To_Follow").rawValue !== null) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Able_To_Follow").rawValue == 1 ? myArrHGN.push(oName + " was able to follow the stimulus") : myArrHGN.push(oName + " was not able to follow the stimulus");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Resting_Nystagmus").rawValue !== null) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Resting_Nystagmus").rawValue == 1 ? myArrHGN.push("Resting Nystagmus was observed") : myArrHGN.push("Resting Nystagmus was not observed");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Lenses_None").rawValue == 1) {
		myArrHGN.push(oName + " was not wearing any corrective lenses")
	} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Glasses").rawValue == 1) {
		myArrHGN.push(oName + " was wearing glasses")
	} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Contacts").rawValue == 1) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Lens_Type").rawValue !== null) {
			if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Lens_Type").rawValue == 1) {
				var contactType = "hard";
			} else {
				var contactType = "soft"
			}
			myArrHGN.push(oName + " was wearing " + contactType + " contacts")
		}
	}

	// LACK OF SMOOTH PURSUIT

	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_L").rawValue == "None") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_R").rawValue == "None")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Lack of Smooth Pursuit was not observed in either of " + oNameS + " eyes");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_L").rawValue == "Present") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_R").rawValue == "Present")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Lack of Smooth Pursuit was observed in both of " + oNameS + " eyes");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_L").rawValue == "None") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_R").rawValue == "Present")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Lack of Smooth Pursuit was not observed in " + oNameS + " left eye but was observed in " + oNameS + " right eye");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_L").rawValue == "Present") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Pursuit_R").rawValue == "None")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Lack of Smooth Pursuit was observed in " + oNameS + " left eye but was not observed in " + oNameS + " right eye");
	}

	// DISTINCT AND SUSTAINED NYSTAGMUS

	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_L").rawValue == "None") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_R").rawValue == "None")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Distinct and Sustained Nystagmus at Maximum Deviation was not observed in either of " + oNameS + " eyes");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_L").rawValue == "Present") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_R").rawValue == "Present")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Distinct and Sustained Nystagmus at Maximum Deviation was observed in both of " + oNameS + " eyes");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_L").rawValue == "None") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_R").rawValue == "Present")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Distinct and Sustained Nystagmus at Maximum Deviation was not observed in " + oNameS + " left eye but was observed in " + oNameS + " right eye");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_L").rawValue == "Present") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Max_R").rawValue == "None")) {
		myArrHGN.push("A Distinct and Sustained Nystagmus at Maximum Deviation was observed in " + oNameS + " left eye but was not observed in " + oNameS + " right eye");
	}

	// ONSET PRIOR TO 45 DEGREES

	var onsetLeftRes = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L").rawValue;
	var onsetRightRes = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R").rawValue;
	if (onsetLeftRes !== null &amp;&amp; onsetRightRes !== null) {
		if (onsetLeftRes == onsetRightRes) {
			if (onsetLeftRes == "None" || onsetLeftRes == "45°") {
				myArrHGN.push("An Angle of Onset Prior to 45° was not observed in either of " + oNameS + " eyes");
			} else {
				myArrHGN.push("An Angle of Onset Prior to 45° was observed in both of " + oNameS + " eyes")
			}
		} else if (onsetLeftRes !== onsetRightRes) {
			if ((onsetLeftRes == "Immediate" || onsetLeftRes == "30°" || onsetLeftRes == "35°" || onsetLeftRes == "40°") &amp;&amp; (onsetRightRes == "Immediate" || onsetRightRes == "30°" || onsetRightRes == "35°" || onsetRightRes == "40°")) {
				myArrHGN.push("An Angle of Onset Prior to 45° was observed in both of " + oNameS + " eyes")
			} else if ((onsetLeftRes == "Immediate" || onsetLeftRes == "30°" || onsetLeftRes == "35°" || onsetLeftRes == "40°") &amp;&amp; (onsetRightRes == "None" || onsetRightRes == "45°")) {
				myArrHGN.push("An Angle of Onset Prior to 45° was observed in " + oNameS + " left eye but not in " + his_her + " right eye");
			} else if ((onsetRightRes == "Immediate" || onsetRightRes == "30°" || onsetRightRes == "35°" || onsetRightRes == "40°") &amp;&amp; (onsetLeftRes == "None" || onsetLeftRes == "45°")) {
				myArrHGN.push("An Angle of Onset Prior to 45° was not observed in " + oNameS + " left eye but was observed in " + his_her + " right eye");
			} else if ((onsetLeftRes == "None" || onsetLeftRes == "45°") &amp;&amp; (onsetRightRes == "None" || onsetRightRes == "45°")) {
				myArrHGN.push("An Angle of Onset Prior to 45° was not observed in either of " + oNameS + " eyes");
			}
		}
	}

	// ANGLE OF ONSET

	if ((xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue !== 'None') &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue !== 'None')) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue == xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue) {
			if (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue == 'Immediate') {
				myArrHGN.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was immediate');
			} else {
				myArrHGN.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was estimated at ' + xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue + ' in both eyes');
			}
		} else {
			var tempOnsetArr = [];
			if (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue == 'Immediate') {
				tempOnsetArr.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was immediate in ' + his_her + ' left eye');
			} else {
				tempOnsetArr.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was estimated at ' + xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue + ' in ' + his_her + ' left eye');
			}
			if (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue == 'Immediate') {
				tempOnsetArr.push('was immediate in ' + his_her + ' right eye');
			} else {
				tempOnsetArr.push('was estimated at ' + xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue + ' in ' + his_her + ' right eye');
			}
			var tempArrayHGN = tempOnsetArr.join(' and ').toString();
			myArrHGN.push(tempArrayHGN);
		}
	} else if ((xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue == 'None') &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue !== 'None' &amp;&amp; xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue !== null)) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue !== "Immediate") {
			myArrHGN.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was estimated at ' + xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue + '° in ' + his_her + ' right eye only');
		} else {
			myArrHGN.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was immediate in ' + his_her + ' right eye only');
		}
	} else if ((xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_R').rawValue == 'None') &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue !== 'None' &amp;&amp; xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue !== null)) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue !== "Immediate") {
			myArrHGN.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was estimated at ' + xfa.resolveNode('topmostSubform.Page1.HGN_Angle_L').rawValue + '° in ' + his_her + ' left eye only');
		} else {
			myArrHGN.push(oNameS + ' Angle of Onset was immediate in ' + his_her + ' left eye only')
		}
	}
	var arrRes = myArrHGN.join('. ').toString() + (".");
	if (arrRes == ".") {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F5.TextField5").rawValue = "";
	} else {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F5.TextField5").rawValue = arrRes;
	}

	//-------------------------------- VGN ------------------------------------------------------/

	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Vertical_Nystagmus").rawValue !== null) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F6.TextField5").rawValue = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Vertical_Nystagmus").rawValue == 1 ? "Vertical Gaze Nystagmus was observed." : 'Vertical Gaze Nystagmus was not observed.';
	}

	//-------------------------------- LOC ------------------------------------------------------/

	if (skipLOC !== true) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F20.TextField5").rawValue = oConvergence == true ? "A Lack of Convergence was observed. " + oNameS + " left eye " + oConvergenceLeft + " and " + oNameS + " right eye " + oConvergenceRight + '.' : "A Lack of Convergence was not observed.";
	}

	//-------------------------------- PUPIL SIZE ------------------------------------------------------/

	var myArrPupils = [];
	var L1Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Room_Light_L").formattedValue);
	var L2Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Darkness_L").formattedValue);
	var L3Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L").formattedValue);
	var Alt1L3Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L1").formattedValue);
	var Alt2L3Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L2").formattedValue);
	var R1Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Room_Light_R").formattedValue);
	var R2Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Darkness_R").formattedValue);
	var R3Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L").formattedValue);
	var Alt1R3Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_R1").formattedValue);
	var Alt2R3Size = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_R2").formattedValue);
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Room_Light_L").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Room_Light_R").rawValue !== null)) {
		if ((L1Size &gt;= 2.5) &amp;&amp; (L1Size &lt;= 5)) {
			var L1Range = "within";
		} else if (L1Size &lt; 2.5) {
			var L1Range = "below"
		} else if (L1Size &gt; 5) {
			var L1Range = "above"
		}
		if ((R1Size &gt;= 2.5) &amp;&amp; (R1Size &lt;= 5)) {
			var R1Range = "within";
		} else if (R1Size &lt; 2.5) {
			var R1Range = "below"
		} else if (R1Size &gt; 5) {
			var R1Range = "above"
		}
		myArrPupils.push("In room light, " + oNameS + " pupils were recorded at " + L1Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm in " + his_her + " left eye which is " + L1Range + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range, and " + R1Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm in " + his_her + " right eye which is " + R1Range + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Darkness_L").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Darkness_R").rawValue !== null)) {
		if ((L2Size &gt;= 5) &amp;&amp; (L2Size &lt;= 8.5)) {
			var L2Range = "within";
		} else if (L2Size &lt; 5) {
			var L2Range = "below"
		} else if (L2Size &gt; 8.5) {
			var L2Range = "above"
		}
		if ((R2Size &gt;= 5) &amp;&amp; (R2Size &lt;= 8.5)) {
			var R2Range = "within";
		} else if (R2Size &lt; 5) {
			var R2Range = "below"
		} else if (R2Size &gt; 8.5) {
			var R2Range = "above"
		}
		var UVLight = (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.UV_Light").rawValue == 1) ? ". While estimating pupil size in near-total darkness, I was unable to clearly visualize the pupils using the red glow of of my penlight with my thumb/finger covering the light. As such, a UV light was used to slightly illuminate the pupils" : "";
		myArrPupils.push("In near-total darkness, " + oNameS + " pupils were recorded at " + L2Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm in " + his_her + " left eye which is " + L2Range + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range, and " + R2Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm in " + his_her + " right eye which is " + R2Range + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range" + UVLight);
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L").presence == "visible") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L").presence == "visible")) {
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L").rawValue !== null)) {
			if ((L3Size &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; (L3Size &lt;= 4.5)) {
				var L3Range = "within";
			} else if (L3Size &lt; 2) {
				var L3Range = "below"
			} else if (L3Size &gt; 4.5) {
				var L3Range = "above"
			}
			if ((R3Size &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; (R3Size &lt;= 4.5)) {
				var R3Range = "within";
			} else if (R3Size &lt; 2) {
				var R3Range = "below"
			} else if (R3Size &gt; 4.5) {
				var R3Range = "above"
			}
			myArrPupils.push("In direct light, " + oNameS + " pupils were recorded at " + L3Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm in " + his_her + " left eye which is " + L3Range + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range, and " + R3Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm in " + his_her + " right eye which is " + R3Range + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
		}
	} else if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L1").presence == "visible") &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L2").presence == "visible")) {
		var altPupilArr = [];
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L1").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L2").rawValue !== null)) {
			if ((Alt1L3Size &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; (Alt1L3Size &lt;= 4.5)) {
				var L3RangeAlt1 = "within";
			} else if (Alt1L3Size &lt; 2) {
				var L3RangeAlt1 = "below";
			} else if (Alt1L3Size &gt; 4.5) {
				var L3RangeAlt1 = "above";
			}
			if ((Alt2L3Size &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; (Alt2L3Size &lt;= 4.5)) {
				var L3RangeAlt2 = "within";
			} else if (Alt2L3Size &lt; 2) {
				var L3RangeAlt2 = "below";
			} else if (Alt2L3Size &gt; 4.5) {
				var L3RangeAlt2 = "above";
			}
			altPupilArr.push("In " + oNameS + " left eye, " + his_her + " pupil size ranged between " + Alt1L3Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm, which is " + L3RangeAlt1 + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range, and " + Alt2L3Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm, which is " + L3RangeAlt2 + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_R1").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_R2").rawValue !== null)) {
			if ((Alt1R3Size &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; (Alt1R3Size &lt;= 4.5)) {
				var R3RangeAlt1 = "within";
			} else if (Alt1R3Size &lt; 2) {
				var R3RangeAlt1 = "below";
			} else if (Alt1R3Size &gt; 4.5) {
				var R3RangeAlt1 = "above";
			}
			if ((Alt2R3Size &gt;= 2) &amp;&amp; (Alt2R3Size &lt;= 4.5)) {
				var R3RangeAlt2 = "within";
			} else if (Alt2R3Size &lt; 2) {
				var R3RangeAlt2 = "below";
			} else if (Alt2R3Size &gt; 4.5) {
				var R3RangeAlt2 = "above";
			}
			altPupilArr.push("In " + oNameS + " right eye, " + his_her + " pupil size ranged between " + Alt1R3Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm, which is " + R3RangeAlt1 + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range, and " + Alt2R3Size.toPrecision(2) + " mm, which is " + R3RangeAlt2 + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
		}
		if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_R1").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_R2").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L1").rawValue !== null) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Direct_L2").rawValue !== null)) {
			var tempArrRes = "\n\n" + altPupilArr.join('. ').toString();
			myArrPupils.push("In direct light, " + oNameS + " pupils were recorded as a range of sizes: " + tempArrRes);
		}
	}
	var arrRes = myArrPupils.join('.\n\n').toString() + (".");
	if (arrRes == ".") {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.PupilSize.F7.TextField5").rawValue = "";
	} else {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.PupilSize.F7.TextField5").rawValue = arrRes;
	}

	//-------------------------------- REACTION ------------------------------------------------------/

	var reaction2light = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Reaction").rawValue;
	var reactArray = [];
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Rebound_Dilation").rawValue !== null) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Rebound_Dilation").rawValue == 1) {
			reactArray.push("Rebound Dilation was observed.");
		} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Rebound_Dilation").rawValue == 2) {
			reactArray.push("Rebound Dilation was not observed.");
		}
	}
	if (reaction2light !== null) {
		switch (reaction2light) {
			case "Normal":
				reactArray.push(oNameS + " reaction to light was normal.");
				break;
			case "Slow":
				reactArray.push(oNameS + " reaction to light was slow.");
				break;
			case "Little":
				reactArray.push(oName + " had little reaction to light.");
				break;
			case "None Visible":
				reactArray.push(oName + " had no visible reaction to light.");
				break;
			default:
				reactArray.push(oNameS + " reaction to light was not recorded because [EXPLAIN].");
				break;
		}
	}
	xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F8.TextField5").rawValue = reactArray.join(' ').toString();

	//-------------------------------- PULSE ------------------------------------------------------/

	var pulse1 = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Pulse1").rawValue);
	var pulse2 = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Pulse2").rawValue);
	var pulse3 = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Pulse3").rawValue);
	var pTime1 = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Pulse1_Time").rawValue == null ? "????" : xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Pulse1_Time").formattedValue;
	var pTime2 = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Pulse2_Time").rawValue == null ? "????" : xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Pulse2_Time").formattedValue;
	var pTime3 = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Pulse3_Time").rawValue == null ? "????" : xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Pulse3_Time").formattedValue;
	var myArrPulse = [];
	if ((pulse1 != 0) || (pulse2 != 0) || (pulse3 != 0)) {
		if (pulse1 != 0) {
			if (pulse1 == "????") {
				var Res1 = "????";
			} else if ((pulse1 &gt;= 60) &amp;&amp; (pulse1 &lt;= 90)) {
				var Res1 = "within";
			} else if (pulse1 &gt; 90) {
				var Res1 = "above";
			} else if (pulse1 &lt; 60) {
				var Res1 = "below";
			}
			myArrPulse.push(oNameS + " first pulse was measured at " + pulse1 + " bpm at " + pTime1 + " which is " + Res1 + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
		}
		if (pulse2 != 0) {
			if (pulse2 == "????") {
				var Res2 = "????";
			} else if ((pulse2 &gt;= 60) &amp;&amp; (pulse2 &lt;= 90)) {
				var Res2 = "within";
			} else if (pulse2 &gt; 90) {
				var Res2 = "above";
			} else if (pulse2 &lt; 60) {
				var Res2 = "below";
			}
			myArrPulse.push(oNameS + " second pulse was measured at " + pulse2 + " bpm at " + pTime2 + " which is " + Res2 + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
		}
		if (pulse3 != 0) {
			if (pulse3 == "????") {
				var Res3 = "????";
			} else if ((pulse3 &gt;= 60) &amp;&amp; (pulse3 &lt;= 90)) {
				var Res3 = "within";
			} else if (pulse3 &gt; 90) {
				var Res3 = "above";
			} else if (pulse3 &lt; 60) {
				var Res3 = "below";
			}
			myArrPulse.push(oNameS + " third pulse was measured at " + pulse3 + " bpm at " + pTime3 + " which is " + Res3 + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
		}
		var arrRes = myArrPulse.join('.\n\n').toString() + (".");
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F9.TextField5").rawValue = arrRes;
	}

	//-------------------------------- BLOOD PRESSURE ------------------------------------------------------/

	var myArrBP = [];
	var sys = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Systolic").rawValue);
	var dia = Number(xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Diastolic").rawValue);
	if (sys != 0) {
		if ((sys &gt;= 120) &amp;&amp; (sys &lt;= 140)) {
			var sysRange = "within";
		} else if (sys &gt; 140) {
			var sysRange = "above";
		} else if (sys &lt; 120) {
			var sysRange = "below";
		}
		myArrBP.push(oNameS + " systolic pressure was measured at " + sys + " mmHg which is " + sysRange + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
	}
	if (dia != 0) {
		if ((dia &gt;= 70) &amp;&amp; (dia &lt;= 90)) {
			var diaRange = "within";
		} else if (dia &gt; 90) {
			var diaRange = "above";
		} else if (dia &lt; 70) {
			var diaRange = "below";
		}
		myArrBP.push(oNameS + " diastolic pressure was measured at " + dia + " mmHg which is " + diaRange + " the " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range");
	}
	var arrRes = myArrBP.join('.\n\n').toString() + (".");
	if (arrRes == ".") {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F10.TextField5").rawValue = "";
	} else {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F10.TextField5").rawValue = arrRes;
	}

	//-------------------------------- BODY TEMPERATURE  ------------------------------------------------------/

	var tempRes = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Body_Temp").formattedValue;
	if ((tempRes != null) &amp;&amp; (tempRes != 0)) {
		if ((tempRes &gt;= 97.6) &amp;&amp; (tempRes &lt;= 99.6)) {
			var tempRange = "within";
		}
		if (tempRes &gt; 99.6) {
			var tempRange = "above";
		}
		if (tempRes &lt; 97.6) {
			var tempRange = "below";
		}
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.F11.TextField5").rawValue = (oNameS + " body temperature was measured at " + tempRes + "°F which is " + tempRange + " the  " + oAverageVsExpected + " DRE range.");
	}

	//-------------------------------- MUSCLE TONE ------------------------------------------------------/

	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Muscle_Tone").rawValue !== null) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Muscle_Tone").rawValue == 1) {
			var muscleTone = "normal";
		} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Muscle_Tone").rawValue == 2) {
			var muscleTone = "flaccid";
		} else if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Muscle_Tone").rawValue == 3) {
			var muscleTone = "rigid";
		}
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_8.ClinicalNOtes.#subform[22].TextField5").rawValue = (oNameS + " muscle tone was " + muscleTone + ".");
	}

	/*==========================================================================================
		9. SIGNS OF INGESTION
	=========================================================================================*/

	var myArrayIng = [];
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Injection_None_Observed").rawValue == 1) {
		myArrayIng.push("No injection sites and/or puncture marks were observed.");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Nasal_Notes").rawValue !== null) {
		myArrayIng.push(oNameS + " nasal cavity was [" + xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Nasal_Notes").rawValue.toLowerCase() + "].");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Oral_Notes").rawValue !== null) {
		myArrayIng.push(oNameS + " oral cavity was [" + xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Oral_Notes").rawValue.toLowerCase() + "].");
	}
	if (skipConj == false) {
		if (oConjunctiva == true) {
			myArrayIng.push("A marked reddening of the conjunctiva was observed in " + oNameS + " eyes.")
		} else {
			myArrayIng.push("A marked reddening of the conjunctiva was not observed in " + oNameS + " eyes.")
		};
	}
	var arrRes = myArrayIng.join(" ").toString();
	xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_9.TextField5").rawValue = arrRes;

	/*==========================================================================================
			10. SUBJECT'S STATEMENTS
	==========================================================================================*/

	var statementArr = [];
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Time_Now").rawValue !== null) {
		statementArr.push(oName + " estimated the time at " + xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Time_Now").rawValue + " when the actual time was " + xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Time_Actual").formattedValue + ".");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Drugs_Used").rawValue !== null) {
		var medStatement = xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Drugs_Used").rawValue.split(',').map(function (reduce) {
			return reduce.trim();
		});
		if (medStatement.length == 2) {
			var medStatement = medStatement.join(' and ').toString();
		} else if (medStatement.length &gt;= 3) {
			var medStatement = medStatement.join(', ').replace(/, ([^,]*)$/, ', and $1').toString();
		}
		statementArr.push(oName + " admitted to using the following drugs and/or medications: " + medStatement + ".");
	}
	var statementArr = statementArr.join(' ').toString();
	xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Notes_10.TextField5").rawValue = statementArr;

	/*==========================================================================================
		11. DRE'S OPINION
	=========================================================================================*/

	var myArrDREOpinion = [];
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Not_Impaired").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.F13.TextField5").rawValue = ("It is my opinion as a certified Drug Recognition Expert that " + oName + " is not impaired, and is able to operate a vehicle safely.");
	}
	if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Medical").rawValue == 1) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.F13.TextField5").rawValue = ("It is my opinion as a certified Drug Recognition Expert that " + oName + " is unable to operate a vehicle safely due to medical impairment");
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Medical").rawValue !== 1) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Not_Impaired").rawValue !== 1)) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Alcohol").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("alcohol")
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.CNS_Depressant").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("a CNS Depressant");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.CNS_Stimulant").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("a CNS Stimulant")
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Hallucinogen").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("a Hallucinogen")
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Dissociative_Anesthetic").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("a Dissociative Anesthetic");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Narcotic_Analgesic").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("a Narcotic Analgesic");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Inhalant").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("an Inhalant");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Cannabis").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrDREOpinion.push("Cannabis");
		}
		if (myArrDREOpinion.length == 1) {
			var arrRes = myArrDREOpinion.toString();
		} else if (myArrDREOpinion.length == 2) {
			var arrRes = myArrDREOpinion.join(' and ').toString();
		} else if (myArrDREOpinion.length &gt; 2) {
			var arrRes = myArrDREOpinion.join(', ').replace(/, ([^,]*)$/, ', and $1').toString();
		}
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.F13.TextField5").rawValue = "It is my opinion as a certified Drug Recognition Expert that " + oName + " is under the influence of " + arrRes + ", and is unable to operate a vehicle safely.";
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Not_Impaired").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Medical").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Alcohol").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.CNS_Depressant").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.CNS_Stimulant").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Hallucinogen").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Dissociative_Anesthetic").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Narcotic_Analgesic").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Inhalant").rawValue == 0) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page2.Cannabis").rawValue == 0)) {
		xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.F13.TextField5").rawValue = "";
	}

	/*==========================================================================================
		12. TOXICOLOGICAL SAMPLE
	=========================================================================================*/

	var myArrSample = [];
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Urine").rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Blood").rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Oral").rawValue == 1)) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Urine").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrSample.push("a urine specimen");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Blood").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrSample.push("a blood specimen");
		}
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Oral").rawValue == 1) {
			myArrSample.push("an oral fluid specimen");
		}
		if (myArrSample.length &gt; 1) {
			var pluralChk = "were";
			var specNum = "specimens"
		} else {
			var pluralChk = "was";
			var specNum = "specimen"
			var arrRes = myArrSample.toString();
		}
		if (myArrSample.length == 2) {
			var arrRes = myArrSample.join(' and ').toString();
		} else if (myArrSample.length &gt; 2) {
			var arrRes = myArrSample.join(', ').replace(/, ([^,]*)$/, ', and $1').toString();
		}
	}
	if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Urine").rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Blood").rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Oral").rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Refused").rawValue == 1)) {
		if (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Refused").rawValue !== 1) {
			xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.F14.TextField5").rawValue = (oName + " consented to provide " + arrRes + " as part of the [arrest/evaluation]. The " + specNum + " [" + pluralChk + " submitted for analysis]. Toxicology results are [pending at the time of this report].");
		} else if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Refused").rawValue == 1) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Urine").rawValue == 1) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Blood").rawValue == 1) || xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Oral").rawValue == 1) {
			xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.F14.TextField5").rawValue = (oName + " refused to provide a specimen as part of the [arrest/evaluation], and " + arrRes + " was obtained from " + oName + " [pursuant to a search warrant]. The " + specNum + " [" + pluralChk + " submitted for analysis]. Toxicology results are [pending at the time of this report].");
		} else if ((xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Refused").rawValue == 1) &amp;&amp; (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Urine").rawValue !== 1) || (xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Blood").rawValue !== 1) || xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page1.Chem_Oral").rawValue !== 1) {
			xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.F14.TextField5").rawValue = (oName + " refused to provide a specimen.");
		}
	}
	xfa.resolveNode("topmostSubform.Page3.Page3_Topmost.Header.Button1").caption.value.text.value = "Recreate Narrative";
}
</script>
                  </event>
               </field>
